<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1958-07-03T09:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1958-07-03T09:00:00-05:00" n="78" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d78">
                        <head>78. Telegram From the <gloss type="from">Embassy in Cuba</gloss> to
                            the <gloss type="to">Department of State</gloss><note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d78fn1">Source: Department of State, Central
                                Files, 737.00/7–358. Official Use Only; <gloss target="#t_NIACT1">Niact</gloss>.</note></head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="italic">Havana</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1958-07-03T09:00:00-05:00"><hi rend="italic">July 3,
                                        1958—9 a.m.</hi></date></dateline></opener>
                        <p>18. Briefly these are facts. Consul <persName corresp="#p_WPF1">Wollam</persName> believes everybody well. Conditions for release
                            are: <list>
                                <label>(A)</label>
                                <item>No more shipment of arms.</item>
                                <label>(B)</label>
                                <item>Complete assurance that naval base will not be used for
                                    supplying arms and munitions.</item>
                                <label>(C)</label>
                                <item>An observer to assure compliance with <gloss target="#t_MDAP1">MDAP</gloss> agreement.</item>
                            </list></p>
                        <p><persName corresp="#p_WPF1">Wollam</persName> states that these people
                            are fanatics with blind spots and determined. <persName corresp="#p_WPF1">Wollam</persName> says he is sure there are
                            Communists in the group but mixed up in thinking.</p>
                        <closer><signed><persName corresp="#p_SEET1"><hi rend="strong">Smith</hi></persName></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>